# TrustShield AI Assets

Place your app assets here:

- `images/` — PNG/JPG images
- `icons/`  — SVG and PNG icons  
- `animations/` — Lottie JSON animation files

## Required Files
- `images/logo.png` — App logo (optional, app uses Icon widget)
- `animations/shield_scan.json` — Lottie animation for scanning (optional)
- `icons/app_icon.svg` — App icon SVG (optional)
